+# Rigging
+
+Project tooling values for Shipshape roles. Values only, not procedure.
+Procedure lives in the skills. Every role reads this on open.
+
+## Stack
+
+- language: JavaScript
+- runtime: Node.js
+- packageManager: npm
+
+## Directories
+
+- implementation: src
+- specs: features
+- verification: features/support
+- assets: data
+- scantlings: none
+
+## Commands
+
+- discover: `cucumber-js --dry-run`
+- focused: `cucumber-js {scenario}`
+- broad: `cucumber-js`
+- coverage: `c8 --reporter json --report-dir coverage cucumber-js`
+- step-usage: `cucumber-js --format usage`
+- plank-inventory: `jsdoc -X src/*.js`
+- typecheck: none
+- lint: none
+
+## Perturbation
+
+- message: `PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed`
+- perturb: `throw new Error("PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed");`
+
+## Tiers
+
+- default: @logic
+- policy: @logic tier uses no external credentials
+- weather: logs/weather.json
+- runrecord: logs/runrecord.json
+
+## Dependencies
+
+- policy: npm default
+- dependency: @cucumber/cucumber ^13.0.0
+
+## Outbound
+
+- outbound: none
